What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is a really fun, interesting class! The readings are limited to the Western canon, but the class benefits from dealing with texts well-within the instructors' expertise. This class is a good opportunity to look at maybe familiar texts through a different lens, and offers lots of opportunity for interdisciplinary connections.
